Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------PREV------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么发现？迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试了各种方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无奈这里的器材有限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 那东西确实了得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体的反应速度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非我军机动战士能比
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定满载着各种超乎想象的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为武器可谓完美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 菲利特那边进展如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初步看来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是强制激发X-Rounder能力的机械
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用脉冲磁场刺激脑内X-Rounder领域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让机师发挥出部分类似X-Rounder的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强制激活X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能会对大脑造成恶性影响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长期使用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早会伤及机师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详情只能等死亡机师的验尸报告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美的机动战士外加
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激发机师X-Rounder能力的头盔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克继续分析
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须报告巨环基地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.91,0:01:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激活X-Rounder的头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了那个头盔 我也能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「维甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是移民计划失败的受害者们…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被遗弃在火星圈的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建立起的新兴国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.92,0:02:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被迫在严酷环境下生活的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为夺回那座名为「地球」的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,策划起了规模宏大的计划
