Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不去看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:03:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等大家看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再慢慢看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为自己明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是看到敌人死掉的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才重新意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们机师随时会死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定就是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…随时都会下达出击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一去不回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不留下遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不留下想做却没做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说！我有事想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说可能会让人觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也没有一起外出过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进餐都在舰上食堂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我想说的是…重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卢斯上士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}结婚好吗～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上士…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没见过这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我用那头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那头盔 如果真可以激发X-Rounder能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 一定能杀更多敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那头盔很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能让你用它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没其他事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有那头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定可以变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是杰哈特…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻略巨环基地的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有责任都在我这个指挥官身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿承受任何处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的计划考虑到了任何一种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨环基地攻略战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最低限度的战略目标已经达成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集到了足够多的素材判断地球军军力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球军的部署
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应变能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-Rounder的战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牺牲不是没有价值的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以那些数据为依据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美的入侵作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美的…入侵作战？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的作战不会失败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们开始吧 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们期待已久的 新世界的构建
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这个节骨眼上禁止出击？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为戈林和泽尔报仇的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长也赞成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下个作战计划成型了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也会重新整编加入战队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军人就必须服从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 您脑子没秀逗吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个毛头指挥官和我们的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个更重要 有得比吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也赞同蕾西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是X-Rounder中的精英
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八魔人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我们做缩头乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与美学相去甚远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是相同意见吗 敏克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 倒不如说我第一个想冲出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己呢？ 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会真的想阻拦我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 这话题很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的话你都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无视命令擅自出击 这可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别紧张嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没说要告发你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上我一起…没意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士出击？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是达乌内斯司令室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人允许他们出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔·加勒特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敏克·雷丁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾西·阿德涅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷奥·路易斯 四人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上让他们回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用 晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,匆忙通信会被联邦察觉我们的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就来 等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无人哨机R-33 S-31
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探测到红移
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无人哨机T30 发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与维甘舰船热谱一致
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 明日野司令料事如神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的目标多半是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺德拉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是地球圈防线上不容有失的中轨道卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括武器生产在内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各功能集于一身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺德拉姆一旦有失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦的战略会土崩瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人侵略地球会变得轻而易举
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以赶忙离开索伦城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦格雷亚斯正率军前往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰也须在作战中出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敌系统有感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B442发现不明机体 数量4
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘的机动战士！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来找你了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 陪我玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔和X-Rounder部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 一级战斗部署
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 一级战斗部署
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士部队紧急出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}重复 全员一级战斗部署…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说黑的那个也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是杰哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 X-Rounder…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆又迟到？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫他动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好 敌人是X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别离开我的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫·安尼克 G-巨人出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开 杂兵们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的对手是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道你在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出来就连船一起砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主炮 速射模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悉数听我指示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射间隔设为每秒1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的行动被看穿了 德西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE-2在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还不出击？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想拿它做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想戴上它战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么傻话！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为击败维甘的X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要对抗X-Rounder的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西会毁了你的脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少胡思乱想 快去机库
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了白的 全是废物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是两台蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克斯少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莉莎 麦克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死去吧 地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华美地散去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命之花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克斯少尉和阿莉莎后退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉来晚了 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就让他返航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能让他继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢 竟敢让我美丽的机体负伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有空东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 X-Rounder的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别瞧不起人 地球种
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 我竟然…这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不美！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷奥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢对雷奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳命来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敏克姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太嚣张了 可恶的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我劣势？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是 八魔人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小瞧人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管你什么预判能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子靠的是技术含量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾西！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 继续孤立无援的战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道自己在干什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是让自己置身于危险中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还可能殃及所有战友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许再违抗命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想当X-Rounder吗？ 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 不那么做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我连父亲 也超越不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成不了X-Rounder的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成为超级机师亚瑟姆·明日野就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级…机师？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是X-Rounder 但却很牛的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次 我干掉了X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你之前也用高达击败过X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做你擅长的就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得更强 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便有优秀的天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心理脆弱自暴自弃也成不了大器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里强的家伙才是最后的赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 别这样 鼻子会痒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用去见德西尔大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不必 作战需要进行调整
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你继续妨碍我们作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须被清除
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的实力 才不是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.47,0:22:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦格雷亚斯中校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看…看那个
